# Part 2 — Describe a piece of technology (not a phone) that you would like to own.

A piece of technology that I would really like to own is a high-performance AI laptop, especially something like a powerful gaming laptop with an advanced GPU. As a computer science student who is really interested in artificial intelligence and robotics, I think this kind of device would be extremely useful for me.

The model I want costs around 15,000 to 20,000 yuan, which is definitely expensive for a university student like me. That’s why I haven’t bought it yet. However, I’m planning to save money gradually or maybe buy it after getting an internship in the future.

If I had this laptop, I would mainly use it for programming, training AI models, and developing personal projects. Right now, many AI-related tasks require strong computing power, especially when working with machine learning or deep learning models. My current laptop sometimes becomes very slow when I run large programs or multiple development tools at the same time.

Another reason why I want to own it is that it could improve both my efficiency and creativity. For example, I want to build intelligent systems and AI agents in the future, and a powerful computer would allow me to test ideas much faster. Besides study purposes, I could also use it for video editing, gaming, and online courses.

What attracts me most is not only the performance itself, but also the opportunities it could bring me. I feel that technology is becoming increasingly important in modern society, and owning advanced equipment can help students like me stay competitive and explore more possibilities in the AI field.

Overall, although it’s quite expensive, I think it would be a worthwhile investment for my future career and personal interests.

